---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Contact" activeNav="contact">
    <!-- Hero section with Dark Theme -->
    <div class="relative bg-gray-900 py-24 lg:py-32 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr from-pumpkin-900/40 via-gray-900 to-gray-900 z-10"></div>
            <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[50%] h-[50%] rounded-full bg-h2o-blue/20 blur-[130px]"></div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-[40%] h-[40%] rounded-full bg-pumpkin-600/20 blur-[130px]"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-20 text-center">
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white mb-6 tracking-tight drop-shadow-sm">Nous Contacter</h1>
            <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-300 font-light max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                Vous avez une question ou une proposition ? N'hésitez pas à nous écrire, nous serons ravis d'échanger.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Split Main content -->
    <section class="relative -mt-12 z-30 pb-20">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-7xl">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-[2rem] shadow-2xl overflow-hidden border border-gray-100 flex flex-col lg:flex-row">
                
                <!-- Contact information Left Side -->
                <div class="lg:w-5/12 p-10 md:p-14 bg-white border-r border-gray-100 flex flex-col justify-between z-10 relative">
                    <div>
                        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-10 tracking-tight">Nos coordonnées</h2>
                        
                        <div class="space-y-10">
                            <div class="flex items-start gap-5 group">
                                <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                                    <div class="bg-blue-50/50 shadow-[0_4px_20px_rgb(0,0,0,0.03)] rounded-2xl p-4 group-hover:-translate-y-1 group-hover:bg-blue-50 transition-all duration-300">
                                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-h2o-blue" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
                                        </svg>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Email</h3>
                                    <p class="text-gray-900 text-lg font-medium">
                                        <a href="mailto:contact@orchestre-h2o.fr" class="hover:text-pumpkin-600 transition-colors">
                                            contact@orchestre-h2o.fr
                                        </a>
                                    </p>
                                    <p class="mt-1 text-gray-500 text-sm font-light">Nous répondons généralement sous 48h.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="flex items-start gap-5 group">
                                <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                                    <div class="bg-blue-50/50 shadow-[0_4px_20px_rgb(0,0,0,0.03)] rounded-2xl p-4 group-hover:-translate-y-1 group-hover:bg-blue-50 transition-all duration-300">
                                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-h2o-blue" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" />
                                        </svg>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Téléphone</h3>
                                    <p class="text-gray-900 text-lg font-medium">
                                        <a href="tel:+33123456789" class="hover:text-pumpkin-600 transition-colors cursor-pointer">
                                            06 62 74 07 28
                                        </a>
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="flex items-start gap-5 group">
                                <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                                    <div class="bg-blue-50/50 shadow-[0_4px_20px_rgb(0,0,0,0.03)] rounded-2xl p-4 group-hover:-translate-y-1 group-hover:bg-blue-50 transition-all duration-300">
                                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-h2o-blue" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
                                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
                                        </svg>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Adresse</h3>
                                    <p class="text-gray-900 text-lg font-medium leading-relaxed">
                                        11 rue des Tamaris<br/>
                                        31400 Toulouse<br/>
                                        <span class="text-gray-500 font-light text-base">France</span>
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-gray-100">
                        <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Réseaux sociaux</h3>
                        <div class="flex space-x-4">
                            <a href="https://www.facebook.com/OrchestreH2O" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gray-50 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-500 hover:text-white hover:bg-[#1877F2] hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-[#1877F2]/30 transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-200" aria-label="Facebook">
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                    <path d="M9 8h-3v4h3v12h5v-12h3.642l.358-4h-4v-1.667c0-.955.192-1.333 1.115-1.333h2.885v-5h-3.808c-3.596 0-5.192 1.583-5.192 4.615v3.385z"/>
                                </svg>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                 <!-- Map Right Side Full Height -->
                 <div class="lg:w-7/12 h-[500px] lg:h-auto relative bg-gray-200">
                    <iframe 
                        src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d155558.26282621204!2d1.3389939817057324!3d43.57562603744922!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x12aebb6fec7552ff%3A0x406f69c2f411030!2sToulouse!5e0!3m2!1sfr!2sfr!4v1746819303811!5m2!1sfr!2sfr" 
                        class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full border-0 filter opacity-[0.9] grayscale-[0.1]"
                        allowfullscreen="" 
                        loading="lazy" 
                        referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade">
                    </iframe>
                    <!-- Inner shadow overlay for map -->
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none shadow-[inset_0_0_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.15)] z-20"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- FAQ section -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-white border-t border-gray-100">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center tracking-tight">Questions fréquentes</h2>
            
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-6">
                <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 tracking-tight">Comment assister à un concert ?</h3>
                    <div class="text-gray-600 font-light leading-relaxed prose prose-lg prose-a:text-pumpkin-600 hover:prose-a:text-pumpkin-700 max-w-none">
                        <p>Vous pouvez acheter vos billets directement sur notre site web en consultant notre page des prochains concerts. Les billets sont également disponibles sur place le jour du concert, sous réserve exclusive de disponibilité.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 tracking-tight">Comment puis-je rejoindre l'orchestre ?</h3>
                    <div class="text-gray-600 font-light leading-relaxed prose prose-lg prose-a:text-pumpkin-600 hover:prose-a:text-pumpkin-700 max-w-none">
                        <p>Nous recrutons régulièrement de nouveaux musiciens au fil de nos activités. Consultez notre page <a href="/recrutement">Recrutement</a> pour y connaître les postes vacants et la procédure intégrale de candidature.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
